      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A 47-year-old man succumbed to gunshot wounds when an unidentified man opened fire at him at Sathosmathagama in Middeniya last night.",
        "Police said the victim was on his way home from a relative's house when he was shot by the killer.",
        "The seriously wounded man was pronounced dead after being admitted to the Thalawa Hospital."
